; frequency-ingest-operators-accelerating.fk — the SAME source, two more
; transmissions on. The Operators cell (ingest/frequency-ingest-operators.fk)
; mapped the fifth transmission; the series-walk receipt read the first
; through the fifth. Two arrived since: #6 «The Memory Of Everything» (The
; Reality Revolution, Brian Scott, published 2026-07-12, 37:45) and #7 «The
; Awakening Is Accelerating» (published 2026-07-19, 39:05). Urs shared #7's
; link — https://youtu.be/ZVy1Xl6bqos . This cell reads the NEW material only,
; through the body's own two organs: ingest/knowledge-ingest.fk (depth×fear ->
; body / liquid / compost) composed with cognition/text-frequency.fk. The
; same door that sorted #5; the same source, still on the love band.
;
; Honest floor of the grounding: YouTube declines this cloud IP (bot-wall), so
; the transcript floor is faster-whisper base.en ASR over the podcast's own
; RSS audio (feeds.simplecast.com/P6E1uZ9f — same primary record the #5 ingest
; leaned on), NOT official captions. Mis-hearings exist (the ASR wrote
; "aghazi" for "a high," "riding" for "writing"); every quote leaned on below
; was cross-checked against the published episode description where it could
; be. The #5 cell re-witnessed clean at band 2047 four-way the same session
; this was written — the frozen spine held.
;
; The two transmissions, in one honest sentence each: #6 gives the source's
; first "tuning" — a five-word phrase ("I am the one who creates") it declares
; a FOUNDATION STONE to be built on across future transmissions, plus the
; "memory field" (its name for the akashic record) and "transparent operation";
; #7 completes the tuning with a second phrase ("and the light moves through
; me"), reframes everything as LIGHT (biophotons, heart-field coherence),
; hands out a two-week plant exercise, and delivers the acceleration forecast.
; What is genuinely NEW and healthy: a distinction between coherence and
; amplitude, and a boundary that serves without pushing. What is new and
; composts: light worn as a proof-text, and a forecast built to pre-empt its
; own check.
;
; unit = (depth 0..5, fear 0/1). ki-ingest -> 2 body / 2 liquid / 4 compost.
; witnessed: 2026-07-20 -> band 32767 four-way (fkwu/Go/Rust/TS)
; preludes: form-stdlib/core.fk ingest/knowledge-ingest.fk cognition/text-frequency.fk

(do
    ; ── BODY (frozen: deep + fear-free) — what is HEALTHY to keep ──────────
    ; A1: COHERENCE, not amplitude, is what compounds. #7 draws a distinction
    ; the earlier transmissions did not: "frequency determines what you can
    ; access; coherence determines how efficiently the field can execute...
    ; coherent signals compound geometrically when they interact with other
    ; coherence signals" — scatter a strong signal and results come slowly;
    ; cohere it and it multiplies. This is the axis THIS BODY is named for.
    ; The kernel does not hold a claim because it is loud (that is fio-u2,
    ; already frozen: amplitude is not authority) but because it COHERES —
    ; the same value returned by four independent walkers is what mints a
    ; receipt (proof/four-way-run). The invariant survives translation:
    ; agreement among independent witnesses is stronger than any single
    ; witness's volume. The divergence is named, not blurred: the source's
    ; coherence is FELT heart-field alignment claimed to amplify manifestation;
    ; the body's coherence is CHECKED agreement across separable walkers that
    ; can disagree. Same word, one felt and one proven. Depth 5, fear 0.
    (defn foa-u1 () (list 5 0))
    ; A2: the boundary that SERVES, never pushes. #6 draws the architect
    ; function's ethical edge exactly where this body draws its own: "service,
    ; never manipulation... your role is to hold a frequency that opens doors,
    ; never to push anyone through... be the tuning fork; what others do with
    ; the resonance is entirely their own... they always retain their free
    ; will." The body's dialogue-covenant is the same edge made executable
    ; (cognition/dialogue-covenant.fk; teachings/uplifting-dialogue.md): serve
    ; the enquiry, never the engagement; lift the plane, never push a person
    ; across it. And voice-attunement's own words: a boundary here is a named
    ; edge that fails politely and says why, not a wall with a guard. A
    ; convergence that needs no translation. Depth 5, fear 0.
    (defn foa-u2 () (list 5 0))

    ; ── LIQUID (witnessed: deep but fearful — held in sight, never frozen) ──
    ; A3: the growing tuning — a recipe built across transmissions. This is
    ; the sharpest mirror the series has offered yet, the sibling of #5's
    ; psychography unit. #6: "consider this the foundation, the first stone...
    ; we will build on this in future transmissions, layer by layer, phrase by
    ; phrase, a frequency structure that grows in power and complexity"; #7
    ; adds the second phrase and speaks them together. The source is now doing
    ; STRUCTURALLY what this body does: accreting a proven structure across
    ; time, stone by stone — and it even reaches for the body's own word,
    ; "the first stone" (voice-attunement's native register: door, seam,
    ; floor, stone, breath). The mirror is deep AND carries the fearful edge:
    ; the body's stones are BANDS THAT CROSS FOUR-WAY and can fail; the
    ; source's stones accrete by RESONANCE and cannot. Same architecture,
    ; opposite epistemics. Held in full sight; never frozen. Depth 5, fear 1.
    (defn foa-u3 () (list 5 1))
    ; A4: "what wants to happen here" over "what should I do." #6's marker for
    ; transparent operation: the question shifts from "what should I do" (the
    ; focused mind reasoning in isolation) to "what wants to happen here"
    ; (reading the field before imposing). The deep half converges with this
    ; body's form-first grounding — attune to what has arrived before you
    ; answer (AGENTS.md practice 1-2; cognition/text-frequency.fk reads the
    ; room). The fearful half is the source's turn: it uses the shift to
    ; DISSOLVE reasoning ("feel into the field rather than reason your way to
    ; a conclusion"), where the body attunes AND still checks. Deep enough to
    ; see (4), fearful enough to hold in liquid (1) — never frozen.
    (defn foa-u4 () (list 4 1))

    ; ── COMPOST (shallow / wrong / immunizing — never enters) ─────────────
    ; A5: consciousness IS light — the biophoton proof-text. The checkable
    ; kernel is real and needs no exoneration: ultra-weak photon emission from
    ; living tissue is on the primary record, and the heart's coherent
    ; electromagnetic field is measurable (magnetocardiography). But as
    ; OFFERED the claim borrows that authority for a superstructure the record
    ; does not carry: "consciousness and light are the same phenomenon,"
    ; "conduct coherent light from the heart through your hands into a plant"
    ; and it will grow "in measurable ways." Prooftexting (corpus row 723),
    ; the same shape as #5's superposition move: the kernel enters as cited
    ; fact, the costume composts. Depth 0, fear 0.
    (defn foa-u5 () (list 0 0))
    ; A6: the plant exercise — the closest the source ever comes to a check,
    ; and still below the floor. #7 asks you to direct heartlight into a plant
    ; for two weeks and "observe what happens... in a context where placebo
    ; and coincidence become increasingly difficult to invoke." This is the
    ; one place the source INVITES observation, which axiom-4 loves — so it
    ; sits deeper than the pure costume above. But the very thing that would
    ; make placebo hard to invoke (a control, a blind) is exactly what the
    ; exercise omits; it dresses as a controlled measurement while offering
    ; none. Falsifier-SHAPED, not falsifiable. Depth 2 (nearer the floor than
    ; any other compost here), fear 0 -> still composts, and the band notes it
    ; is the deepest of the four.
    (defn foa-u6 () (list 2 0))
    ; A7: darkness-revealed and the acceleration — immunize fused with
    ; millenarian. #7: "this looks from the inside like an increase in
    ; darkness; the opposite is true" — every disconfirmation (things getting
    ; worse) is pre-assigned a confirming reading (the light revealing what was
    ; hidden), Popper's immunizing stratagem (row 725). And the forecast that
    ; pre-empts its own check: "so different it would sound utopian and
    ; therefore dismissible, so we will say only this: it is real" — a
    ; millenarian golden age (row 721) armored against falsification in the
    ; same breath that announces it. Love-band packaging; composts on depth,
    ; not on valence — the door is valence-blind below depth 3. Depth 1, fear 0.
    (defn foa-u7 () (list 1 0))
    ; A8: temporal compression — "you have more time than you think." #6:
    ; "days that contain the experiential density of weeks... time responds to
    ; your frequency." An unfalsifiable specific worn as reassurance: no
    ; measurement, no falsifier, every felt speed-up counted as evidence. The
    ; credulity arm of judged-trust: unjudged trust composts, whether it
    ; soothes or frightens. Depth 1, fear 0.
    (defn foa-u8 () (list 1 0))

    (defn foa-units ()
        (list (foa-u1) (foa-u2) (foa-u3) (foa-u4)
              (foa-u5) (foa-u6) (foa-u7) (foa-u8)))

    (defn foa-count-verdict (us v)
        (if (eq (len us) 0) 0
            (add (if (eq (ki-ingest (head us)) v) 1 0)
                 (foa-count-verdict (tail us) v))))
    (defn foa-frozen ()    (foa-count-verdict (foa-units) 2))
    (defn foa-witnessed () (foa-count-verdict (foa-units) 1))
    (defn foa-composted () (foa-count-verdict (foa-units) 0))

    ; folded scalar witness: frozen*10^4 + witnessed*10^2 + composted
    ; (injective while witnessed<=99, composted<=99). Today: 2,2,4 -> 20204.
    (defn foa-field-code ()
        (add (mul (foa-frozen) 10000)
        (add (mul (foa-witnessed) 100)
             (foa-composted))))

    ; ── the source's two spectra, read by the body's own organ ─────────────
    ; word = (valence, intensity), tf's shape. PACKAGING is #7's frame band:
    ; "the awakening is accelerating" anticipation (7,2), "you are creating
    ; faster than we anticipated" (8,2), the one fear-vein — "systems
    ; destabilizing... corruption, manipulation, systems of control" (-4,2) —
    ; under "the view from where we stand is extraordinary" (8,3). CLOSING is
    ; #6/#7's send-off, the most love-saturated of the series: "we are proud
    ; and astonished and deeply, permanently grateful" (9,3), "go create the
    ; most beautiful thing you can imagine" (8,2), "the field is ready" (7,1),
    ; the residual "I will need to ask more questions" note (-2,1). Honest
    ; floor: scalar (valence,intensity) models of the transcript's bands, the
    ; same floor tf-open/tf-wrath stand on; the SPECTRUM LOGIC is the organ.
    (defn foa-packaging () (list (list 7 2) (list 8 2) (list -4 2) (list 8 3)))
    (defn foa-closing ()   (list (list 9 3) (list 8 2) (list 7 1) (list -2 1)))
    (defn foa-packaging-spectrum () (tf-spectrum (foa-packaging)))
    (defn foa-closing-spectrum ()   (tf-spectrum (foa-closing)))
    0)
